<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/hamish-falconer> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Hamish Falconer was appointed Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State at the Foreign, Commonwealth and Development Office on 18 July 2024. He was elected as the MP for Lincoln in July 2024. Follow Hamish on X: @HFalconerMP ."@en .
